let's not make any changes yet. here's some ideas to consider:
- the anti-stuck logic needs to be reworked entirely, but i don't think that's what broke the bot behavior in v45.6.10 compared to v45.6.9, because since the bot logic should have remained unchanged, nothing would have broken the bot behavior that was fine in v45.6.9. so you  need to dive into this more deeply.
- update 45.6.10 also didn't satisfy my request for more score and style titles, so i'll be more specific. currently the score titles of only "terminated, eliminated, vanquished, ascended, transcended" are nowhere near enough. we need 20 of these, so get to brainstorming. similarly, style titles (soldier, veteran, etc.) and combo titles (relentless, unstoppable, mythic) are too few and far in between. we need to vary even more to make sure each session's achievements and titles feel unique.

actually, everything in v45.7.2 was good, except for the teleport marker. you did bring it back, but not make it thicker; instead you just made the ring bigger and the holographic diamond smaller, i think? 

v45.7.2a will just be for bringing that back. small steps.

i don't know what part of the code was the design for the tp marker, but here's the full html code from a previous version that i had backed up elsewhere. so here's what to do:

1. first just extract the tp marker design from it to replace your current implementation. also point out for me which part of the code was what we needed.
2. because asking you to make the lines thicker didn't work out, we're instead just going to add more lines to it. we already have the shapes of the bouncing base ring and holo rotating diamond, so just keep those and add more wireframe lines to fill out more details. you know what i mean.
3. notice how in the recovered design, the bouncy frequency of the 3d diamond and the pulsating frequency of the base ring don't match. so help me change that.

with that in mind, here's the full code:

index.html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Neon Blade: Melee Arena v45.6.7</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Dots&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; overflow: hidden; background-color: #111; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; user-select: none; transition: background-color 0.5s; }

        /* --- CYBERPUNK HUD (Compact) --- */
        #ui-layer {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
        }

        #crosshair {
            position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; width: 32px; height: 32px;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(22.5deg); 
            opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.1s;
            z-index: 5;
        }
        #crosshair svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(51, 204, 255, 0.8)); }

        /* Top HUD */
        #hud-top { 
            padding: 15px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .hud-right-col {
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 6px;
        }

        .hud-panel {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid #33ccff;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
            font-style: italic;
            transform: skewX(-15deg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(51, 204, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }
        .hud-panel-content { transform: skewX(15deg); }

        #score-display { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #33ccff; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); }
        #mode-display { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #aaa; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        /* FPS Display - Thicker Font v45.6.4 */
        #fps-display {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; 
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #111; /* Dark Text */
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* Light BG, low opacity */
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Dark Border */
            padding: 2px 10px;
            transform: skewX(-15deg);
            display: none;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .fps-inner { transform: skewX(15deg); }

        /* Bottom HUD */
        #hud-bottom { 
            padding: 25px; display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-end; 
        }

        .stat-group {
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
        }
        .stat-header {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-left: 5px;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; color: white;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #000;
        }
        #lives-display {
            color: #ff3333; font-size: 1rem; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ff0000;
        }

        .bar-frame {
            width: 250px; height: 18px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transform: skewX(-20deg);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .bar-fill {
            height: 100%; width: 100%;
            transition: width 0.1s linear;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        #health-fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #cc0000, #ff3333); box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff3333; transition: all 0.1s; }
        #stamina-fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0066cc, #33ccff); box-shadow: 0 0 10px #33ccff; }

        .health-critical {
            animation: pulse-red 0.5s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-red {
            from { box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff0000; filter: brightness(1); }
            to { box-shadow: 0 0 25px #ff0000; filter: brightness(1.5); }
        }

        /* Ability Icon */
        .ability-group { margin-left: auto; transform: skewX(-10deg); }
        .ability-icon { 
            width: 60px; height: 60px;
            border: 1px solid #fff; 
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
            font-weight: bold; color: white; 
            transition: 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .ability-icon-inner { transform: skewX(10deg); text-align: center; }
        .ability-icon.active { 
            border-color: #00ffaa; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ffaa; color: #00ffaa; 
